{
  "stem": "14737.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Inside, in the room, in the middle, they had a very big dish as a toilet, so people-- whoever want to in that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the morning, I've seen some people went to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They came out and ask if who wants to go to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I understand Bergen-Belsen wasn't a camp to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And who is going to work will get a piece of bread or will get, in the evening, some soup.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "At one point, I also-- I'm going to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They took me to a place, the little-- it wasn't a farm, but they had grass.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They had to take out the grass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We had about 100 people or over 100.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There came a German SS man, what I've seen with my eye, and started to hit a young Jew there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Wanted to kill him, but they didn't want to kill him, just plainly shoot him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He wanted-- he made up his mind he is going to kill him for [? a reason. ?] He didn't kill him completely, but the man, as we finished work, couldn't go home.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He wasn't on his feet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He ordered four people should take him on his shoulders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He was close to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The rest were also to death-- Muselmann.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Were-- and we came back to camp on the plantation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "All those who went to work will get some piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They lined up those who weren't in for bread, and I thought also I was in that line, but people who didn't go to work also mixed in there, because with the yard, you couldn't find out.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "By the time I came there, was no bread, was no food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "One day, they tried it with three people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I still had a little strength there myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
